{
  "chapter": 167,
  "chapter_summary": "第167章「公子多情」。寇仲夜探酒铺时遭遇魔门高手辟尘道长，辟尘以善人面目出现试图探查和氏璧下落，被寇仲错有错着骗过。跋锋寒告知寇仲辟尘实为魔门妖道，三十年前横行北方。随后\"多情公子\"侯希白上门为师妃暄索取和氏璧，与跋锋寒先礼后兵对饮论扇，谈及侯希白扇面上八位美女独缺师妃暄之因。二人最终交手，剑扇交锋势均力敌。寇仲醒来点明和氏璧不在手上，暗示三人可联手，侯希白收扇停战。本章展现魔门势力介入和氏璧之争，以及侯希白的风流多情与高超武艺。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宁道奇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_chen",
      "speaker_name": "道人",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "宁道兄久已不问世事，你们尚未有那个资格。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bi_chen",
      "text": "道长如何称呼？法驾光临，有何指教？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_chen",
      "speaker_name": "避尘道长",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "贫道避尘，今趟来是想为我们道门尽点心力。只要你肯把取去的东西交出，贫道会为你化解与慈航静斋和净念禅院的仇怨，保证他们绝不再予追究。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bi_chen",
      "text": "若我真有盗宝，不如由我亲手送回去，何用道长你大费唇舌？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_chen",
      "speaker_name": "避尘道长",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "因为我知你根本不肯交回宝物，所以才要来管这件事。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bi_chen",
      "text": "道长既自称避尘，为何忽然又有闲心来管尘世的事？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_chen",
      "speaker_name": "避尘道长",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "问得好，贫道今次动了尘心，皆因不忍看着千古以来唯一能勘破《长生诀》的两朵奇花，就这么因人世的权位斗争而毁于一夕之间。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bi_chen",
      "text": "原来道长有此心胸，请恕我寇仲年少无知，但如若我坚持不交出宝物，道长会否亲手来毁了我呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_chen",
      "speaker_name": "避尘道长",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你的脑筋转得很快。不如这样吧！我背着你挡你十刀，若你不能迫得我落往天井，你便乖乖的把和氏璧交出来，让贫道为你物归原主，把事情圆满解决。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bi_chen",
      "text": "请恕我不能答应。并非因欠此把握，而是即使道长胜了，我也拿不出和氏璧来，此事绝无虚言，不知道长肯否相信。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_chen",
      "speaker_name": "避尘道长",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇仲你可知道自己已臻练虚合道的道家至境，欠的只是火候吧了！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bi_chen",
      "text": "甚么叫练虚合道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_chen",
      "speaker_name": "避尘道长",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我道门修练，共分四个阶段，就是练精化气，练气化神，练神还虚，练虚合道。其中过程怎都说不清楚，如人饮水，冷暖自知。要知人的潜力无论如何庞大，总有尽头极限。所以前两个阶段，指的都是肉身的修练。唯有后两个阶段，练的却是如何与充盈于宇宙之间的道相结合；故能超脱肉身，达至入圣合道的化境。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bi_chen",
      "text": "我们练《长生诀》时，似乎打一开始就是道长说的后两个阶段的境界。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_chen",
      "speaker_name": "避尘道长",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这是贫道没法明白的事。现在该怎样解决这事呢？因眼前形势，一不小心，就会引起佛道邪三家之争。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bi_chen",
      "text": "坦白说，就算我真有和氏璧在手，也绝不会交出来。像和氏璧这等宝物，唯有德者居之，谁有本事，便该属谁，若要拿宝，就凭真本领来索取吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_chen",
      "speaker_name": "避尘道长",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你很像贫道年青时的性子，好吧！我再不管此事了！你们好自为之。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子真是个乐天派，惹得我也记起自己多晚没睡！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "坐下再说。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "你的神情为何如此沉重，是听到刚才那避尘的话吗？一看便知那是有德行的道门前辈哩！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "今趟你偏偏看走了眼，此人叫'妖道'辟尘，而非避尘，三十年前曾横行北方，无恶不作，是魔门数一数二的高手，声望仅次于'阴后'祝玉妍，幸好和氏璧真的不在你手上，否则刚才你定给他探出虚实。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "你怎能如此清楚他的来历，我却从没有听过他的名字。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "关于魔门的事，你说是谁告诉我的呢？辟尘虽与祝玉妍同是魔门，但各属不同的流派，平时勾心斗角，但对着外人时却颇为团结。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "这妖道真厉害，连半分邪气都没透出来。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若非我知道魔门有这么一号人物，也会像你般给他骗倒。只从这点，便可知此人修养道行之高，已达登峰造极的境界。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "他是否真能背着来挡我十刀呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这是绝无可能的，连宁道奇都不行。他只是想诈出和氏璧是否在你手上，现在反被你错有错着的骗了。最后一番话表面好听，骨子里却是推波助澜，希望我们和了空一方先拚个两败俱伤，卑鄙之极。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "还有甚么像他这类的高手，不若你一并说出来给我听，让我心中有个准备。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不要自己吓自己好吗？至少在子时前，他也不会再来烦我们，那时有命再说吧！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "我倒有个消息提供，传闻曲傲和突厥的'龙卷风'突利准备联手来对付我们，又是一场不易对付的硬仗。我们是否须改变做英雄好汉的计划，转而研究如何落荒逃命呢？",
      "tone": "担忧",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你认为在现今的情势下，我们仍可搭船坐车地轻易离城吗？你留心听一下，外面静如鬼域，行人们都到那里去了？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "难道有人把街道封锁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "虽不中亦不远矣。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们是否该向子陵学习，好好睡上一觉？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "这提议最合朕意，唉！有人骑马来了！是否过早一点呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "子时前来的是朋友，子时后则是敌人，你看我猜得是否准确。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "干扰我睡眠的则朋友也变敌人，有甚么事由你出头应付好了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你真够朋友。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们三个给我滚出来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "来者何人！我跋锋寒今夜不杀无名之辈。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "跋兄请恕在下一时冲动之下口出粗言。如若跋兄肯化干戈为玉帛，交出和氏宝璧，让在下归还妃暄小姐，在下愿为刚才惹怒跋兄的话敬酒道歉。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "我最讨厌说话兜兜转转的人，阁下究竟是何方神圣，竟要代师妃暄出头？",
      "tone": "不耐烦",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "听跋兄的语气，交回和氏璧的事是没有得商量哩！那只好动手见个真章。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "原来是'多情公子'侯希白，难怪如此落力护花，失敬失敬。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "实不相瞒，在下一向对三位心仪向往，绝不愿在这样的情况下碰头。咦！寇兄和徐兄不是受了伤吧？还是在睡觉呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "侯兄不用理会他们，大家初次相识，不若先喝两杯，然后动手，如何？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "这叫名副其实的先礼后兵，让在下先敬跋兄一杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "闻名不如见面，跋兄没有令在下失望。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "侯兄的摺扇以精钢为骨，不知扇面却是用甚么材料造成？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "这个问题我还是首次碰到，跋兄的眼力真厉害。敝扇乃采天蛛吐的丝织成，坚勒无比，不畏刀剑。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "好兵器，只不知上面是否绘有师妃暄的画像呢？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "此扇独欠妃暄小姐，跋兄可猜到原因吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "这个该不难猜，一是她气质独特，侯兄感到难以把握；又或侯兄用情太深，反患得患失，无从着墨。",
      "tone": "从容",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "跋兄提的这两个原因都有点道理。在我来说，却是不知该以她那个神态入画，才能表现她至美之态，故一直犹豫，未敢动笔。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "这番话比甚么赞美更能令人动心，不如侯兄一口气在扇面上画出十多个师妃暄来，每个代表她一种姿态神韵，不就可把难题破解？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "那恐怕要画无穷尽的那么多个才成，如此对她可太不敬了。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "说得精彩，跋某人敬侯兄一杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "此事能否和平解决？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "侯兄少说废话。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "跋兄一向不过问家国之事，为何独要卷入眼下这无谓的争端中，得到宝璧于跋兄有何用处？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "落雁是个很寂寞的女孩子，那一天当我采来一朵白菊花，为她插在头上时，她便露出这既惊喜但又落漠的伸色。当时她定是想起别人。我不但没有嫉忌，还把她那一刻的神情画下来。只有这神情才最能代表她。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "text": "跋兄比我想像中要厉害多了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_feng_han",
      "speaker_name": "跋锋寒",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "彼此！彼此！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "侯希白你这是何苦来由，和氏璧根本不在我们手上，就算在我们手上，我们也可以撇开他娘的江湖规矩，先联手把你宰了。",
      "tone": "不耐烦",
      "chapter": 167,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 375
    }
  ],
